{"word":"μέλει","slug":"μέλει","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μέλει</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μέλω\">μέλω</a></el> ‘be an object of care/thought’] this 3 <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sg.\">sg.</a> form occurs in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> always <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ dat.\">dat.</a> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gener.\">gener.</a> signifies <b>be of interest to, be of concern to <a href='B:470 22:16'>Mt 22:16</a>; <a href='B:480 4:38'>Mk 4:38</a>; <a href='B:480 12:14'>12:14</a>; <a href='B:490 10:40'>Lk 10:40</a>; <a href='B:500 10:13'>J 10:13</a>; <a href='B:500 12:6'>12:6</a>; <a href='B:510 18:17'>Ac 18:17</a>; <a href='B:530 9:9'>1 Cor 9:9</a>; <a href='B:670 5:7'>1 Pt 5:7</a>.</b> Abs. <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μή\">μή</a> σοι μελέτω</el> don’t be concerned about it <b><a href='B:530 7:21'>1 Cor 7:21</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Μελεά\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:μελετάω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}